.TH PRODBOX_host 1
.SH NAME
prodbox-host \- Host prerequisite checks
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B prodbox host
.SH DESCRIPTION
Host diagnostics and public-edge validation.
.SH SUBCOMMANDS
.TP
\fBensure-tools\fR
Verify required host tools
.TP
\fBcheck-ports\fR
Check required ports
.TP
\fBinfo\fR
Display host diagnostics
.TP
\fBfirewall\fR
Check firewall requirements
.TP
\fBpublic-edge\fR
Check public DNS/TLS edge state
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
\fBprodbox host info\fR
Render host information.
